title: Jay Pharoah And Adam Pally: Licensed To 'Champaign ILL'
description: Saturday Night Live alum Jay Pharoah looks back on his early stand-up days and shows off his celebrity impressions in a game with actor Adam Pally. This episode originally aired January 4, 2019.
